p_notification_preference.notification_message: Create alert rules for your vehicles and geofences. Choose event(s) (Vehicle Moving/Stopped, Ignition On/Off, Geofence Enter/Exit, Fuel Increase/Decrease, Over Speed), pick delivery channel(s) (Push, Email, WhatsApp, SMS), and select users / vehicles / geofences. Turn Status = On to start receiving alerts.

p_report_preference.report_message: Schedule reports to be delivered automatically. Enter a Report Name, choose Report Type (Daily / Weekly / Monthly), select the Report List and Email recipients, and set Status = On to start delivery.
